When emails are active on this bulletin, You will receive an email with a link that contains the code needed for a new password. If you click that link then another email message will be sent to you with the random password in it.

If for some reason you did not click the forgot password link from this bulletin then you can delete the email message and your password will not be changed.

When you have received the random password, you should login and change your password to something easy for you to remember but difficult for others to obtain.